29
00:02:48,400 --> 00:02:49,360
[SPEAKER_00] I očekujem to tako.

30
00:02:49,599 --> 00:02:51,840
[SPEAKER_00] Tako sam i zamišljao ujutro kad sam se probudio.

31
00:02:52,960 --> 00:02:56,000
